headline: Ulta Beauty (NasdaqGS:ULTA) Partners With Beyoncé's Cécred For Nationwide Haircare Launch
summary: Ulta Beauty (NasdaqGS:ULTA) saw a price move of 1% over the last month, potentially influenced by the recent partnership with Cécred, Beyoncé Knowles-Carter's hair care brand, marking a significant exclusive launch in the company’s history. This collaboration involved prominent in-store branding and salon integrations across all locations, aiming to attract a larger customer base. Despite broader market volatility, with major indices like the Dow Jones and S&P 500 experiencing sharp declines...
